      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="cs-label">COLLABORATORS</div>
        <div class="cs-text">CEO, CTO, engineers, and pet-service businesses</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="u-mt-clamp-sm">
      <div class="cs-media cs-ar-3-1">
        <img class="modal-target" src="diagram_my_role.svg" alt="Business opportunities, technical constraints, and provider operations converging through the designer’s role into a coherent product model.">
      </div>
      <div class="cs-media-caption">As the sole product designer, I worked closely with the CEO and CTO to understand the business need behind each request, identify the essential use cases, and design the simplest model that could support them without creating another layer of product complexity.</div>
    </div>
